   KOSOVO-CLARK (Washington) _ The general running the campaign to
end the murder and expulsion of Kosovo's Albanians learned as an
adult that his grandfather was a Russian Jew who fled the pogroms a
century ago. A profile. By Elizabeth Becker.
</P>
<P>
   ARK-BOAT-SINKS (Hot Springs, Ark.) _ Death toll at 13 tourists
in sinking of amphibious boat in this resort town. At the scene,
however, it's like nothing happened. By David Firestone.
</P>
<P>
   SOCSEC-BALL-PROFILE (Washington) _ Profile of Robert Ball, old
lion and voice of traditionalism in the Social Security debate. By
Robin Toner.
</P>
<P>
   With photo.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-DEVILS-PENGIUNS (Pittsburgh) _ Jaromir Jagr, who missed four
games with an injury, scored the winning goal in overtime Sunday _
after tying the game with 2:12 left in regulation _ as his
Pittsburgh Penguins forced a seventh game by beating the New Jersey
Devils 3-2.
</P>
