<P>
   POW-JACOBS (Los Angeles) _ Rabbi Steven Jacobs of L.A.'s Temple
Kol Tikva, who has been a close associate of Jesse Jackson for
years, accompanied Jackson on his mission to free the American POWs
in Serbia. By Michael Coit. (Will move in the ``n'' California and
``a'' national news files.)
</P>
