<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-02 21:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1499 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SAFIRE-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      05-02 0734
