<P>
   BUCHANAN-CHINA (Seattle) _ China is ``not remotely qualified''
to become a member of the World Trade Organization and the United
States should not yield to ``bribes'' such as those offered by
Premier Zhu Rongji on his recent visit to the United States,
Republican presidential candidate Patrick Buchanan said Sunday in
